    "body": "We do support multiple logs in the PR but not an arbitrary `n` of the same type. For now you could do:\r\n```solidity\r\nfor (uint256 i = 0; i < n; i++) {\r\n    vm.expectEmit(false, false, false, false);\r\n    emit Transfer(address(this), address(this), 0);\r\n}\r\nbatch.doTransfers();\r\n```",
